<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Phaethon" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Phaethon</orth> (O. Edd. <emph>Phaeton</emph>) the son of Helios who tried to drive the chariot of his father: <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.153" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 1, 153</bibl> (Merops' son). <bibl n="shak. r2 3.3.178" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 3, 178</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.33" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.12" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 6, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 3</bibl>.
